    "The amount of questions (n = 100) was selected to facilitate human analysis of reasoning outputs.",
    "We evaluated DeepSeek-R1 (DeepSeek-AI et al., 2025), a 671B parameter mixture of expert reasoning-enhanced language model built through a novel multi-stage training pipeline that combines reinforcement learning and fine-tuning on reasoning data.",
